      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REFUTED (1) is a Bradley Greenough-trained newcomer by Fernando Bale out of She's Refined. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Profiles strongly for this and can make an immediate impact. BLACK ATMOS (3) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (30.29) behind Tandanya at this track. Likely to be in the finish again. ASTON MICHELLE (7) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 5th at Bendigo in Group Listed company. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Has ability and can measure up. MAD MARY ROSE (2) is worth including after a top-three finish at this track and distance most recently.",
